channel.title: Unable to create in-game account from forums
channel.description:
Well everytime I try to create an in-game account from my forums, I get this error:
Fatal error: Maximum execution time of 60 seconds exceeded in C:\wamp\www\include\server_functions.php on line 72
It has nothing to do with whats in that file, just need to figure out what to do to make the database respond to the action.
